**The canonical princess cut combination:**
- **Diamond:** 1ct, G color, VS1 clarity, table 68–72%, depth 65–70%, L:W 1.00–1.02, Polish Excellent, Symmetry Excellent
- **Setting:** [Comfort Fit Solitaire in Platinum — item 316236](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/comfort-fit-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-316236?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) — $1,790 — 1,107 reviews
